Changes V1.10 ---> V1.10a
=========================


Easylife Extension
------------------

  - HUGE BUG FIX: Previous release was assembled with no error messages!
 
  - Version number of last release was left at 1.09, and not incremented
    to 1.10
    

AmosGuide.AMOS
--------------

  - BUGFIX: Now correctly accepts a filename & nodename in command line$ 

  - Improved documentation 

  - Now opens file selector if AMOSPro_Help.Guide is not found when run
    from Help menu

  - BUGFIX: When you click on a link to the same page you are already on
    the page is not redisplayed, and is not added onto the retrace queue
    again.
    
    
VarChecker.AMOS
---------------

  - Removed defunct attempt to show varchecker.doc & replaced it with
    on-line context sensitive help using AmosGuide.

  - Improved documentation
  
     